    <!-- Missed in the P0-05 sweep (occupancy/equipment/ventilation/shading/
         result/result_component got this pattern; snapshot didn't): any
         User-group member in the same company could otherwise read/write
         any other user's snapshot. Caught while adding the job/artifact
         rules below, since a job references a snapshot the same way a
         result does. -->
